e she is on TV, just stop what you are doing and listen to her — then consider she is half of Dave or my age.</p><p> Anyway, we had a blast talking about, well <em>everything</em> . Dave<del> included the entire 167 minutes</del> edited it down to under a half-hour, which makes this very listenable.</p><p> It was a lot of fun spending time with this crew over the weekend, and I am already looking forward to the trip next year.</p><p></p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://ritholtz.com/2023/08/on-the-road-to-camp-kotok/">On the Road (to Camp Kotok)</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://ritholtz.com">The Big Picture</a> .</p> ;
